# type: Content of: <title>
#. type: Content of: <title>
msgid ""
"Patent Reform Is Not Enough - GNU Project - Free Software Foundation (FSF)"
msgstr ""
"Une r&eacute;forme des brevets n'est pas suffisante - GNU Project - Free "
